  # circe
  
  [![Build status](https://img.shields.io/github/workflow/status/circe/circe/Continuous%20Integration.svg)](https://github.com/circe/circe/actions)
  [![Coverage status](https://img.shields.io/codecov/c/github/circe/circe/master.svg)](https://codecov.io/github/circe/circe)
